{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "6f1b873b-4c4a-4d12-92da-5ee27f682e76",
    "name": "Bulk Generate Coupons",
    "description": "Given a CSV file of coupons, this collection may be used to bulk generate coupons against a Coupon Promotion in a BigCommerce store.\n\nBefore using, configure your values for the following collection variables:\n\n| **Variable** | **Value** |\n| --- | --- |\n| api-token | Your BC API token |\n| store-hash | Your BC store hash |\n| promotion-id | The promotion ID for a Coupon Promotion in your store |\n\nTo use, first produce a CSV file with a single column. The column should have the header \"code\" and each row should contain exactly one unique coupon code. Use the CSV file as a data source in Collection Runner. For more information, see the [Postman documentation](https://blog.postman.com/using-csv-and-json-files-in-the-postman-collection-runner/)\n\nConsider using a utility like this one to generate your CSV file: [https://github.com/hatertron3000/coupon-generator](https://github.com/hatertron3000/coupon-generator)",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "createdAt": "2021-09-21T15:05:20.000Z",
    "updatedAt": "2022-01-14T22:45:56.000Z",
    "lastUpdatedBy": "45334",
    "uid": "45334-6f1b873b-4c4a-4d12-92da-5ee27f682e76"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "Create Coupon Code",
      "event": [
        {
          "listen": "prerequest",
          "script": {
            "id": "5c50d81a-74d1-4cde-8325-57dad89bdf5f",
            "exec": [
              ""
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        },
        {
          "listen": "test",
          "script": {
            "id": "96419963-3cb1-4daf-b335-30224d53ffa3",
            "exec": [
              "pm.test(\"Status code is 201\", function () {",
              "    pm.response.to.have.status(201);",
              "});"
            ],
            "type": "text/javascript"
          }
        }
      ],
      "id": "7fa8161a-098d-4c06-b31a-9f11314a82d9",
      "protocolProfileBehavior": {
        "disableBodyPruning": true
      },
      "request": {
        "method": "POST",
        "header": [
          {
            "key": "X-Auth-Token",
            "value": "{{api-token}}",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Accept",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "key": "Content-Type",
            "value": "application/json",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ],
        "body": {
          "mode": "raw",
          "raw": "{\n    \"code\": \"{{code}}\",\n    \"max_uses\": 1,\n    \"max_uses_per_customer\": 1\n}"
        },
        "url": {
          "raw": "https://api.bigcommerce.com/stores/{{store-hash}}/v3/promotions/{{promotion-id}}/codes",
          "protocol": "https",
          "host": [
            "api",
            "bigcommerce",
            "com"
          ],
          "path": [
            "stores",
            "{{store-hash}}",
            "v3",
            "promotions",
            "{{promotion-id}}",
            "codes"
          ]
        }
      },
      "response": [],
      "createdAt": "2021-09-21T15:05:31.000Z",
      "updatedAt": "2022-01-14T17:15:17.000Z",
      "uid": "45334-7fa8161a-098d-4c06-b31a-9f11314a82d9"
    }
  ],
  "event": [
